{"tid":1434390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 如何應對大埔遊行反對通知書","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T02:46:32.000Z","uid":244133,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c33435dab8691d22adfca4ea75fb7e4678b75476","tid":1434390,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:22:11.000Z","msg":"而家吹到所有鋪頭都閂晒 又咩封路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大埔地勢麻麻 馬路得兩條路走 一係<strong>吐露港</strong> 一係去<strong>粉嶺上水元朗</strong> 其他就得<strong>火車</strong> 但係你地都知黨鐵幾識玩 得閒又唔停呢個站 得閒又唔停嗰個站 佢想點玩都得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以如果到時真係有咁多制肘都真係要諗吓點搞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c815f529cc4664de4e99b9979d983235fc4f413b","tid":1434390,"uid":244133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:24:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家記住切勿失焦！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nPtyKf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nPtyKf.jpg&h=214e4850&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c6b8e22b3d633e3d314f26e1b5437ce18e8873","tid":1434390,"uid":244133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:25:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家記住切勿失焦！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nPtyKf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nPtyKf.jpg&h=214e4850&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d983f41ce6f91d6ce9a9debfe6be49bf2603576f","tid":1434390,"uid":179402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:27:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幫幫手推一推」黑警唔單止搜身時恐嚇市民 仲要強光照市民對眼！ | LIHKG</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=ed3f732b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=e1d6ad73\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有乜野必要同理由對市民使用強光照住佢對眼？呢個行為有咩意義同對工作上有咩幫助？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">強烈要求黑警回應點解要用惡劣 粗暴 令人不適嘅態度 語氣 行為 去對待配合黑警工作嘅市民！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa466c3d905d71c539de798cf8a480fc9d17d601","tid":1434390,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"0579a78f615c509c44a8abfb75cb3e941a59d0b9","tid":1434390,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"改路線<br />\n大埔行去大學站"},{"pid":"ca709ff4a5ae070568454ff15e5ac04b76b2fbae","tid":1434390,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0579a78f615c509c44a8abfb75cb3e941a59d0b9","tid":1434390,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"改路線<br />\n大埔行去大學站"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fd46519c2d8ab211b2fe0079a19292dabd6612","tid":1434390,"uid":236663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:3