Time":"2019-08-08T18:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b43649ffb32d9f6cfb97311f4f69470eed17e52","tid":1434390,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec8e27132aa5eb88cfe06197bfaefdd5568784a","tid":1434390,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c0f335da50d5fa6450b8e0b1029cd4285e086b","tid":1434390,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:05:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b90c41e8123e823d76b5ed48ce2f382671cbf1b7","tid":1434390,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:11:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家覺得加返deadline升級好唔好？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n依家情況同上一個月差多<br />\n又係做好多嘢令到<span style=\"color: red;\">行動失去咗個目的</span>同埋冇時限搞到好似好迷失方向，和理非定勇武定包圍，行動上都係冇共識<br />\n加返deadline有好處<br />\n1.重申五大訴求，目標清晰，行動出師有名<br />\n2.訂立短中期行動計劃，例：今個禮拜和理非回合，唔回應就下個禮拜升級勇武行動<br />\n3.有計劃容易整合文宣<br />\n4.自己人有清晰目標，喺啲狗每日shift focus之下叫人專注返都易啲"}]}